entries.arrival_phase_1: We are locking on to the Inquisitor leading the attack now, stand by for coordinates.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Got him, intercept and terminate the Imperial scum!
entries.assassinate_success: Great work my friend. This should cause unease among the Imperial forces.
entries.escort_remaining: Brother Ezkiel: < Good job pilot, destroy them all! >
entries.escort_wiped_out: Brother Ezkiel: < Excellent, now for the head slime. Get that inquisitor! >
entries.failed_escape: He got away! We are trying to come up with a new plan, get back to base immediately!
entries.quest_location_d: The Dantooine system is relatively free of the Imperial curse but in the area you are heading to, they are launching an attack so they will be everywhere.
entries.quest_target_d: Inquisitors are dangerous and ruthless individuals armed with the best of gear and heavily guarded. If you manage to terminate him, it will wreak havoc with the morale of the Imperial ranks as Inquisitors are considered untouchable among the soldiers of the Empire.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < We're already reaping the benefits of the Inquisitors demise. An Imperial Officer wants to defect and need a safe escort. Stand by for coordinates. >
entries.title: Dantooine system: Terminate the Inquisitor.
entries.title_d: The Imperial Inquisition is launching an attack on one of our space stations in the Dantooine system. We have located the leader behind the attack and it is our hope that you will be able to eliminate him my friend.
